Package: crestree
Title: Analysis of branching branching trajectories from single-cell data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
  person("Ruslan", "Soldatov", email = "Ruslan_Soldatov@hms.harvard.edu", role = c("cre","aut")),
  person("Peter", "Kharchenko", email = "peter_kharchenko@hms.harvard.edu", role = c("aut")))
Description: The package implements a method to reconstruct transcriptional tree from single-cell data using principal graph approach and provides a set of routines to analyze expression patterns associated with the tree. The package also implements a set of routines to analyze bifurcation points of the tree. 
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
